<section id="bug-stats">
<title>Statistics</title>
<body>

<p>
The Gentoo community uses Bugzilla (<uri
link="http://bugs.gentoo.org">bugs.gentoo.org</uri>) to record and track
bugs, notifications, suggestions and other interactions with the
development team.  Between 24 December 2006
and 31 December 2006, activity on the site has resulted in:
</p>

<ul>
<li>540 new bugs during this period</li>
<li>309 bugs closed or resolved during this period</li>
<li>18 previously closed bugs were reopened this period</li>
<li>123 closed as NEEDINFO/WONTFIX/CANTFIX/INVALID/UPSTREAM during this period</li>
<li>154 bugs marked as duplicates during this period</li>
</ul>

<p>
Of the 10703 currently open bugs: 27 are labeled 'blocker', 92 are labeled
'critical', and 428 are labeled 'major'.
</p>

</body>
